            <td bgcolor="#e6e6e6"><font face = "Verdana" size = "2"><b>
Yesterday was off to ssra, and you know what that means, outstanding mob placement<br>
<img src = "http://personal.ghguild.com/hammeron/placement.jpg"><br>
<p>
We did, however, finally get a shot at the Cursed and on our first attempt made a long-overdue killing<Br>
<img src = "http://personal.ghguild.com/hammeron/cursed.jpg"><br>
<p>
Amid many many killings of AOW and XTC, you can finally count the number of hate-giving weapons we have on 2 fingers!  As a guild, the reaction was calm and uninterested<br>
<img src = "http://personal.ghguild.com/hammeron/reaction.jpg"><br>
<p>
Remf showing off his new shiny toy... no more using 2hs for you!<br>
<img src = "http://personal.ghguild.com/hammeron/remf.jpg"><br>
<p>
Shanelle picked up the awesome circlet thing and Zeea won the tunic<br>
<img src = "http://personal.ghguild.com/hammeron/zeea.jpg"><br>
<p>
Congrats to all of you!  Blood was up so we also took a whack at him for some easy loot<br>
<img src = "http://personal.ghguild.com/hammeron/blood.jpg"><br>
<p>
Grats Grap on the mace and Kaasa on the earring!  Well that was yesterday, I'd like to leave you with this, isn't rock sexy as a wood elf?<br>
<img src = "http://personal.ghguild.com/hammeron/rzuk.jpg"><br>
