            <td bgcolor="#e6e6e6"><font face = "Verdana" size = "2"><b>
Last night we ushered in a new year, but first we have a few things to take care of from last year, the completion of three epics these last few days<br>
<p>
<img src = "http://personal.ghguild.com/hammeron/beolesepic.jpg"><br>
<p>
<img src = "http://personal.ghguild.com/hammeron/genepic.jpg"><br>
<p>
<img src = "http://personal.ghguild.com/hammeron/mezzepic.jpg"><br>
<p>
Big congratulations to all three of you!<br>
<p>
And now on to 2003.  Small rant here, is it just me has a holiday that was already rather mundane and pointless lost any significance it might have had by the fact that
we've now celebrated a new <u>millenium</u>... <i>twice</i>.  Oh well, happy new year and best wishes to you, your friends and your family.<br>
<p>
Here's my new years gift to you... a picture of Aramus the hobbit!<br>
<img src = "http://personal.ghguild.com/hammeron/aramus.jpg"><br>
